sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C  as Caller
    participant G  as AXME Cloud Endpoint
    participant AZ as Access Enforcer
    participant P  as Policy / Intent Store
    participant AU as Audit Trail

    C  ->> G:  API request (GET / resume / controls / policy / resolve)
    G  ->> AZ: evaluate api-key + bearer + owner scope + role/grants

    alt not authorized
        AZ -->> G: deny
        G  -->> C: 403 forbidden
    else authorized
        AZ -->> G: allow
        alt read operation
            G  ->> P:  read intent state
            G  -->> C: 200 response
        else mutation operation
            G  ->> P:  compare expected_policy_generation
            alt CAS mismatch
                P  -->> G: stale generation
                G  -->> C: 409 conflict
            else CAS match
                P  -->> G: apply mutation
                G  ->> AU: write audit event
                G  -->> C: 200 updated state
            end
        end
    end
